rows.label: qev060601_MSG0001
rows.name: Hello. *fsssh* Um, are you a Zaruboggan?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_JNK0010
rows.name: Explain

rows.label: qev060601_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Orleron that you're not a Zaruboggan.

rows.label: qev060601_JNK0020
rows.name: Play Along

rows.label: qev060601_SEL0021
rows.name: Say that you may, in fact, be a Zaruboggan.

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0002
rows.name: Not a Zaruboggan... *fsssh* Okay, got it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0003
rows.name: You seem really nice. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0004
rows.name: You are one? *fsssh* Okay, got it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0005
rows.name: ...Er, was that a joke? *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0006
rows.name:
Um, hey! *fsssh* Did you know that I'm Orleron
and I'm a Zaruboggan? [ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0007
rows.name:
*fsssh* So I have to devoltanize.
It's my duty![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0008
rows.name:
But to do that, I need a new gorkwa, and there aren't
any around here. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0009
rows.name:
Do you know gorkwas? *fsssh* The staves you use to
devoltanize? Where are they?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_JNK0050
rows.name: Query

rows.label: qev060601_SEL0051
rows.name: Ask Orleron to tell you more about gorkwas.

rows.label: qev060601_JNK0060
rows.name: Answer

rows.label: qev060601_SEL0061
rows.name:
Tell Orleron that you've seen
other Zaruboggan with them.

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0010
rows.name:
Zaruboggan use gorkwas to fulfill their sacred duty!
But there aren't any here. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0011
rows.name:
But that's their gorkwa! Not my gorkwa. *fsssh*
I need a new one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0012
rows.name:
Will you bring me a new gorkwa? *fsssh*
That way I can finally be a grown-up![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0013
rows.name: *fsssh* And then I can fulfill my sacred duty![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0014
rows.name:
Okay, I'll wait. I can study about how to be a good
grown-up until you come back. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0015
rows.name:
But, um, where should I study?
*fsssh* Can you tell me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_JNK0030
rows.name: Suggest NLA

rows.label: qev060601_SEL0031
rows.name: Tell Orleron to study with the humans in New LA.

rows.label: qev060601_JNK0040
rows.name: Suggest the Ma-non Ship

rows.label: qev060601_SEL0041
rows.name:
Tell Orleron to study with the other
Zaruboggan in the Ma-non ship.

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0016
rows.name:
Okay, got it. *fsssh* I'll study how to be a grown-up
with...yoomans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0017
rows.name:
Okay, got it. *fsssh* I'll study how to be a grown-up
with Zaruboggan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0018
rows.name:
Please find me a new gorkwa. *fsssh* I'll learn how to
do my sacred duty in the time it takes you to get it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0021
rows.name:
So I'll be studying in Noo El Lay. *fsssh*
I'll be waiting for you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0022
rows.name:
I don't really know much about gorkwas either. *fsssh*
Just, um... Just that I need one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0023
rows.name: If I have a gorkwa, I can fulfill my sacred duty! *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060601_MSG0024
rows.name:
So I'll be studying with the Zaruboggan. *fsssh*
I'll be waiting for you![ST:wait ]
